      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, what? I don't follow. \"Goblins\"? I'm looking for technical reasons for a connection timeout in a microservices architecture. Can you please skip the metaphors and give me a serious diagnostic analysis of why the `payment-gateway-auth` service is timing out under load?",
